<strong>Rakusha Cloak - AC 10</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/back.shtml">Back</a><BR>
Weight: 0.1 - HUM<BR>
Classes: <a href="/monk/armour/back.shtml">MNK</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/haste.shtml?spellID=683">Haste</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(Sv Magic +10) (Sv Fire +10) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in the Plane of Hate by Innoruuk.<BR>

