<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Brokenarra LifeFist</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-28 13:51:52</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Seeing as I possess a Cloak of Rushaka, I will comment on what I have discovered.<BR>
<BR>
It's haste is 38%. That means on a lvl 50 Monk (10% natural haste) the overall haste is 48%.<BR>
Flying kick's delay goes from 9 seconds (for a lvl 50 monk) to 5 seconds.<BR>
<BR>
This is one of THE best cloaks in the game, and I for one am glad that it's Monk only.<BR>
A fitting tribute to Monks that die pulling over and over in the Plane of Hate.<BR>
<BR>
Brokenarra LifeFist<BR>
Monk of the Fiftieth Ranking<BR>
Tunare</font></td></tr></table>
